Dialogs.Dialog: How does it look? I thought you'd prefer the shorter one but, does look good on me?
How do you like my hair. I tried shortening it, but...
Fufu. A shorter hair style is cuter... I'm kidding.
This time I tried to make it semi-long. I'd like to hear your thoughts.
I thought about it a lot, and I decided to leave it this long... Does it look weird?
I thought this length was the best, but what do you think?
I tried this 'cause my hair has grown, but what do you think? Mama told me it looks good... Does it look good?
I tried letting my hair grow. This way I would look more like a girl...
How does this hairstyle look? I stretched it out thinking that you might be happy.
Thank you. I'm so happy to be praised.
I'm glad. I've always been curious about what you'd think.
Right? Fufu... No, I'm getting shy.
I see... Okay, I'll use it as reference next time.
I see... I should have stopped before doing this.
Did I fail? What should I do now?
I changed my hair style. What do you think?
I tried to change my hair style to bright my mood.
Hey, did you notice it? What do you think?
I'm glad I'm trying a lot of things...
Thank you. It's closer to what you like?
Ah, it that so? I get it.
Didn't you like it? I think I'll reconsider it then.
...So it's not the one. It was hard choosing after all.
How about this color? I tried it as a change of image.
I changed the color of my hair. Compared to before, what do you think?
I changed the color of my hair. How about it, do you like it?
You know, I changed the color of my hair a little.
Mama tried to stop me, but I thought it would look good on me... So?
You know, I tried this hair color...
I know I been adventurous. So, let's be honest here.
Hey... What do you think about this?
About this color of hair, of course. Are you surprised?
Does this dress look good? It's different from usual, so I don't know myself...
Sometimes I want to wear clothes like this... Do you think they look good?
How about these clothes? I tried to look at a different magazine from usual.
▲主人公＊▲. What do you think of these clothes? I tried to make my image a little cleaner.
I wonder if clean fashion suits me... What do you think?
What do you think of clothes like this? The theme for it was neat and clean girls... I'm kidding.
I wanted to change the atmosphere a little. Don't you think this dress is cute?
I'm tried to wear something different than usual... Do you like clothes like this?
I tried to change my image. Did I get cuter?
I tried to wear casual clothes. Do you like this?
Did my image change a bit? If I wear this kind of clothes, will I look more active?
Depending on whether are you active or not...
How about this outfit? I feel different from usual, so I tried to make it more casual.
This is my best... Do you feel excited about this?
You know, do you think this outfit is... Is it se... Sexy?
I'm a little worried about where you are staring, but... Would you be happy if I wear this kind of clothes?
Do you like this? I'll remember it.
I'm so happy... I was nervous until I showed it to you.
My image change succeeded. I'm glad.
Thank you for your honest opinion. *Phew*
I see. Then this is wrong... Fashion is difficult.
Is that so? I still don't seem to understand you then...
Sorry. If you're not interested, it's fine.
You're not interested then. It might be more of a shock that being told it doesn't suit me.
Even though I decided hesitantly, but this was kind of stupid anyway...
It doesn't make sense if you're not happy...
... I don't think that kind of attitude is good... Geez.
My outfit... Do you think it stands out?
That kind of image might not be good
I always try to dress neatly. What do you think?
Hey, what kind of clothes do you like? How about a clean feeling for today?
I like these cute clothes, but I want to hear your opinion.
What do you think of these clothes? Is cute suitable for your tastes?
I'm trying to dress cutely, but aren't you getting tired of it?
I think casual clothes are good. What do you think?
It's easy to move in when I'm wearing this kind of clothes... What do you think?
Shall I try a different kind of fashion? Maybe it's not just casual I must do.
Okay, if you're okay with it, that's fine... Yup, it's okay. I'm kidding.
Really? I'm glad, but if you like something else, tell me please?
I see... Then, I'll continue to dress this way.
Ah, I see. The next time I go shopping, I'll think about it.
I knew it... I was wondering if that was the case.
That so...? Okay, I'm looking forward for next time.
Hmm... I just wanted a clearer opinion...
I wanted you to see me in a different light...
